(PA-5795) Update Checkout GitHub Action

September 11, 2023.

This commit updates all instances of the Checkout Action from v3 to
v4.

commit.message:
(PA-5341) Add Ruby 3.2 to rspec test matrix

This commit adds Ruby 3.2 to the GitHub Actions rspec test matrix
for both Linux and Windows.

(PA-5341) Update minimum Ruby version to 2.7

This commit updates the minimum version of Ruby to run semantic_puppet
from 1.9.3 to 2.7.0 in the gemspec, and updates the README to reflect
that change.

(maint) GitHub Actions Housekeeping

commit.message:
(maint) Updates Rubies in test matrix

This commit removes the end-of-life Ruby 2.5 from the spec testing
matrix in GitHub Actions, as it is no longer used by any supported
version of Puppet.

This commit also updates JRuby to 9.4.2, the current version used
in puppetserver

(maint) Replaces Snyk with Mend

Puppet has recently moved from Snyk to Mend for vulnerability
scanning.

This commit deletes the Snyk GitHub Action and replaces it with one
for Mend.

(maint) Updates end-of-life Actions and OSes

This commit updates the operating system of Ubuntu runners used
in GitHub Actions from 18.04 (which GitHub is sunsetting in April
2023) and the actions/checkout Action from v2 to v3.
Update CODEOWNERS

commit.message:
Clear module_dependencies when resolving

In 82ffe3aa64bfb785c68539b1688eeb7213ddb96d @module_dependencies was
introduced, but it was never cleared. Since it's a global variable, this
meant that subsequent runs could leak data from previous runs.
